lead_paragraph: NEW ORLEANS - Tim Tebow's career at Florida began when he chose the Gators on national television, the culmination of a television documentary about him. Before he'd ever started a game in college, he had women following him everywhere.
snippet: Now that he's transitioning to the next phase of his career, two questions will linger about Tim Tebow.
